70" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="达蒙·阿尔本和雷猫。图片来源：Ovidio Gonzalez 和 Burak Cingi，来源：GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Damon-Albarn-and-Thundercat.-Credit-Ovidio-Gonzalez-and-Burak-Cingi-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artsits/damon-albarn">达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn)</a>最近与<a href="/artists/thundercat">Thundercat</a>一起登上舞台，并表演了一些独奏曲目和一首<a href="/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a>歌曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/thundercat-review-live-in-london-a-sonic-journey-across-his-discography-3613661">Thundercat 在伦敦的现场演出：跨越他的唱片的声音之旅</a></strong></li></ul><p>4 月 5 日星期五，这位 Gorillaz 主唱出现在 Thundercat 在伦敦 KOKO 场地为期四晚的驻场活动的第三晚，这是他英国巡演的一部分。</p><p>阿尔本在演出即将结束时加入了贝斯手。他们一起表演了《Oh Sheit It&#39;s X》、《Funny Thing》、《Them Changes》和 Gorillaz 的《Cracker Island》，这是动画乐队同名专辑中的主打歌曲，Thundercat 最初出现在该专辑中。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">这群人被安乐死了吗，就像他们知道雷猫和达蒙·阿尔本在他们面前玩饼干岛<a href="https://t.co/bJMLD0aVwX">pic.twitter.com/bJMLD0aVwX</a></p><p> - 塔拉 (@d